Daily fees are only charged once. A team of mammets will sow seeds, water plants, and collect a yield of up to 50 per crop. Entrust the produce producer with care of the following crop? ※Care will be halted in the following circumstances: 　・Seafarer's cowries are insufficient. 　・Yields have reached the maximum of 50. ※Care and associated fees will resume automatically once required conditions have been met. ※Yields harvested via the gardening service will not provide island EXP.

The portrait feature allows you to use a variety of poses, motions, and framing options to compose the perfect portrait of your character.

You may create a different portrait for each gear set, to be displayed at the beginning of certain competitive content like Crystalline Conflict PvP matches or Doman mahjong.

Additional information is available in the portrait guide, accessible from the Portraits window.
